f the core.  The isolation transformer shall be mounted on rubber isolation pads to prevent 60 Hz hum of the core from being transmitted to the base.  The transformer core clamp shall be grounded to the base through a 1" copper strap.  The transformer ins
\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 u\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 \hich\f0 lation system shall be 220\'b0\loch\f0 
